{"tid":2342043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"CY輸咗比賽 評判最低分 但佢值得更多","createTime":"2020-12-26T20:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T09:51:54.000Z","uid":13825,"like":54,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"df1b8230b920800bb3c67623c25a4b5dc687e2fe","tid":2342043,"uid":13825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T20:08:23.000Z","msg":"有追開呢季做星<br />\nCY開頭冇咩表現 一路以嚟剩係知佢唱得下歌<br />\n造星個個參賽者都各有所長<br />\n係團體賽唔識跳舞 比Viu啲剪接剪到佢好似特登跳得差咁<br />\n明明隊友被foul佢自責到唔敢同teammate講嘢自己縮埋一邊 個隊友仲要唔係佢投票投走<br />\n<br />\n直到Trouble maker佢換左look 開始留意到佢<br />\n一樣都係唔識跳舞 但係佢又唔會令我覺得反感<br />\n<br />\n佢對答直率 或者可以話係唔識講嘢 我反而覺得幾討好<br />\n但係香港呢個地方就變左係唔尊重老細 一路睇其實佢好尊重彭秀慧 不停多謝佢<br />\n<br />\n今晚決賽佢表演唔敢話最好 但一定唔會係最低分<br />\n成晚最穩定果個就係佢<br />\n<br />\n不過都係果句 香港地 你唔識講嘢 氹唔掂老細 就比最低分<br />\n<br />\n我只係覺得 呢個𡃁仔絕對唔應該係十強包尾"},{"pid":"f92cdd0e324af4bbee32352cbfe1879ae1bfa30c","tid":2342043,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T21:25:54.000Z","msg":"有十強仲想點"},{"pid":"aeeab743f4e33c5f3c42002e8af91fffb5813b04","tid":2342043,"uid":355064,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T21:36:08.000Z","msg":"邊位 ? 振英 ??"},{"pid":"1a9b14e10afd5e44353259fd22d96bd2adaf2a1d","tid":2342043,"uid":120660,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T21:57:02.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰<br />\n呢樣已經唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc6c5531260c4efcef7f52d2f9da7e88b7c4022","tid":2342043,"uid":34256,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1a9b14e10afd5e44353259fd22d96bd2adaf2a1d","tid":2342043,"uid":120660,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T21:57:02.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰<br />\n呢樣已經唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T22:19:50.000Z","msg":"講樣衰ansonbean應該包尾先啱<img 